1. echo 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/conf/all/arp_accept 

2. Starting scapy as root.

3. Created an ether packet:
a=Ether()
a.show() *this will show you what the variable now has for defaults*
a.src= "Your MAC Address"
a.dst= "ARP requests are broadcast"
a.type= The hex code for ARP

4. Create an ARP packet:
b=ARP()
b.op= opcode for requests
b.hwsrc= "Your MAC"
b.psrc= "Your IP"
b.pdst= "Target IP"

5. Starting TCPDUMP....
